<p>Join the Idaho Conservation League for an <strong>exciting <em>Wild Idaho! 2013</em>. </strong>Our keynote speaker Dr. James Weatherby will speak about conservation and politics in Idaho. He was director of the Public Policy Center at Boise State University and coauthored <em>The Urban West: Managing Growth</em> and <em>Decline and Governing Idaho: Politics, People and Power</em>. <p>On Saturday afternoon, you can <strong>select from a number of fascinating field trips!</strong> As always, we&#39;ll have a <strong>rip-roaring time Saturday evening</strong>. Our silent auction begins late in the afternoon, with a banquet, live auction and socializing to follow.<p>Participants who sign up for lodging generally share cabins, equipped with beds, pillows, bathrooms and showers. You&#39;ll need a sleeping bag and towel. <strong>Dogs are not allowed at Redfish Lake Lodge</strong>.<p>If you have not been an ICL member in the past, you receive a one-year introductory membership with your registration.<p>With all the registration options below, we hope you find the one that suits you! <strong>If not, give Natalie a call</strong> and she&#39;ll set you up. Here are also some helpful links:<ul><li>Agenda (we may update it periodically)<li><a href=\"http://www.redfishlake.com/about-redfish/map/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Directions to Redfish Lake Lodge</a><li><a href=\"http://www.redfishlake.com/camping-information/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Camping information</a></li></li></li></ul></p></p></p></p></p></p>','','Visit EventBrite.com for pricing.','2013-05-17 17:00:00','2013-05-19 12:00:00','2013-04-04 04:00:36','2013-04-09 06:51:56','evdb','http://eventful.com/stanley_id/events/wild-idaho-2013-conference-registration-/E0-001-055788502-9?utm_source=apis&utm_medium=apim&utm_campaign=apic','2013-04-10 03:00:44',3,0),('E0-001-055792859-1',1,'V0-001-000139485-3','Limp Bizkit','','','$30.00 - $85.00','2013-05-21 20:00:00',NULL,'2013-04-04 05:44:59','2013-04-04 05:44:59','evdb','http://eventful.